            <p class="pt6">
                帕维奇通过这本小说创造了一种辞典文体。
                (<a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_fiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/review/5759536/">思郁评论</a>)
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>


            


    <li class="clearfix">
        <a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_nonfiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/subject/20429677/">
        <img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s24515818.jpg" alt="大数据时代" class="cover" />
        </a>
        <h2>
            <a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_nonfiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/subject/20429677/">大数据时代</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="entry-star-small clearfix">
            <span class="allstar40 star-img fleft">
            </span>
            <span class="font-small color-red fleft">
                8.1
            </span>
            <br />
            作者:&nbsp;
            [美] 维克托•迈尔•舍恩伯格（Viktor Mayer-Schönberger）著
            <br />
            大数据&nbsp;/&nbsp;互联网
        </p>
        <div class="entry-list-col2-review color-gray">
            
            <p class="pt6">
                “大数据就是我们可以在更大规模的数据上做到更多我们无法在小规模数据基础上完成的事情。”
                (<a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_nonfiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/review/5704181/">星腾评论</a>)
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>


            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <ul class="clearfix">
            


    <li class="clearfix">
        <a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_fiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/subject/19965972/">
        <img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s24428402.jpg" alt="我读书少，你可别骗我" class="cover" />
        </a>
        <h2>
            <a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_fiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/subject/19965972/">我读书少，你可别骗我</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="entry-star-small clearfix">
            <span class="allstar40 star-img fleft">
            </span>
            <span class="font-small color-red fleft">
                7.5
            </span>
            <span class="fleft ml8">新上榜</span>
            <br />
            作者:&nbsp;
            马伯庸
            <br />
            小说&nbsp;/&nbsp;中国文学
        </p>
        <div class="entry-list-col2-review color-gray">
            
            <p class="pt6">
                马伯庸的博学、想象力、幽默感在这本书里展露得淋漓尽致。
                (<a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_fiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/review/5741308/">石榴评论</a>)
            </p>
        </div>
    </li>


            


    <li class="clearfix">
        <a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_nonfiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/subject/20389202/">
        <img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s24517627.jpg" alt="唐朝穿越指南" class="cover" />
        </a>
        <h2>
            <a onclick="moreurl(this, {from:'pop_nonfiction'})" href="http://book.douban.com/subject/20389202/">唐朝穿越指南</a>
